Package: tenkR
Type: Package
Title: Extract SEC EDGAR Financial Statements into Excel
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your Name", email = "your@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and formats 10-K financial statements (income statement,
    balance sheet, and cash flow statement) from the SEC EDGAR database into
    a clean, formatted Excel workbook. Companies can be identified by ticker
    symbol or company name.
